docs.lead_paragraph: 8 P.M. (ABC Family) THE DUKES OF HAZZARD: THE BEGINNING (2007). April Scott, who hails from Poplar Bluff, Mo., the so-called gateway to the Ozarks, plays Daisy Duke in this made-for-television prequel based on the series about a couple of rabble-rousing Southern cousins. Jonathan Bennett plays Bo Hazzard, Randy Wayne is his cousin Luke, and Christopher McDonald gets gussied up in white as Boss Hogg. Willie Nelson, who played Uncle Jesse in the 2005 Jessica Simpson-Johnny Knoxville big-screen version, reprises the role here.
